-  --format hybrid \
-  --enable-raw \
-  --apply-profile-config \
-  --apply-profile-logs \
-  --duration 60
-```
-
-## Note
-
-MowgliNext garde seulement l'integration robot et les chemins locaux. Toute la logique de validation live, de reset, de profils et de parsing de capture appartient desormais au repo `UM982Driver`.
+If you need receiver-specific live validation for a UM982, use the tooling maintained outside this repository and do not treat it as a MowgliNext runtime dependency.
